== English ==
=== Noun phrase ===
'''[[daylight]] [[savings]] [[time]]'''
# [[daylight saving time]]

==== Usage note ====
Many editors [[replace]] this phrase with [[daylight saving time]], with no "s" after "saving". Some sources, such as the [http://www2.ncsu.edu/ncsu/grammar/Nouns3.html North Carolina State University's Online Writing Lab], state that the form "daylight savings time" is [[incorrect]]. The justification is that "[[saving]]" is a [[present participle]], and this "[[time]]" is for saving daylight; thus it is incorrect to use the [[plural]] noun "[[savings]]".